entity is <i>yours</i>.</span> <span>Use it.</span></h2><p><i>We build on what you already own, harnessing your proprietary customer data to connect with customers. And when you focus on what matters, you move quicker — at the pace of your customers, and at the speed of life. </i> <a href="https://www.signal.co/customer-identity-solution/" class="red-btn"><span>The Customer Identity Solution is here.</span> <span class="ico"></span></a></p></div></div></div><div id="scroll-btns"> <a href="#" class="start-scroll"><span class="ico"></span></a> <a href="#story7" class="scrollto"><span class="ico"></span></a></div></div></div><div class="blue-ring1 blue-ring"></div><div class="blue-ring1a blue-ring"></div><div class="blue-ring2 blue-ring"></div><div class="blue-ring2a blue-ring"></div><div class="blue-ring3 blue-ring"></div><div class="blue-ring3a blue-ring"></div><div class="blue-ring4 blue-ring"></div><div id="story6-cover" class="cover"></div></div><div id="section7" class="section with-overflow" data-section="7" data-anchor="story7"><div class="overflow-content" data-index="7"><div id="pin7"></div><div id="clients"><h2 class="mobile-title">Clients</h2><div class="row middle-xs"><div class="col-xs-12"><div id="quotes" class="swiper-container"><h2>Clients</h2><div class="swiper-wrapper"><div class="swiper-slide"><div class="wrapper"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8220;Signal is one of the pillars of our first-party data asset. Using Signal&#8217;s unique ID, we will be able to tie together multiple different unique IDs in our analytic system across devices and browsers using authentication events based in the Signal platform.&#8221;</span></p><div class="meta"><div class="logo" style="background:url(https://www.signal.co/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/crocs-logo.jpg) 50% no-repeat;"></div><div class="info"><p class="person">Ben Hemphill</p><p class="company">Crocs                                                        , Director Of Digital Marketing And Analytics</p